_sText:
This is one of my older maps that I came across, not one of my greatest but a fun map never the less. 

Both teams start out underground and press the button to rise out of the ground like in the gladiator movie. there is a buyzone all the way up (hint: first team to push the buttom gets to the top first). Hope you like it.

This map is bot ready.

**DO NOT EDIT OR CHANGE ANY PARTS OF THIS MAP WITHOUT MY PERMISSION

** I don't mind people using this map on their server just as long as they give me the IP so that I may play as well =)
